org.apache.hadoop.hbase.wal

类 WALSplitter.OutputSink

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.wal.WALSplitter.OutputSink
  • 封闭类:
    WALSplitter

    public abstract static class WALSplitter.OutputSink
extends Object
    The following class is an abstraction class to provide a common interface to support different ways of consuming recovered edits.

        返回:

      • keepRegionEvent

        public abstract boolean keepRegionEvent(WAL.Entry entry)
        Some WALEdit's contain only KV's for account on what happened to a region. Not all sinks will want to get all of those edits.
        返回:
        Return true if this sink wants to accept this region-level WALEdit.
